Fresh case of gang rape and murder of a student, Grace Oshiagwu, 21 years of age, occurred in Ibadan, Oyo State, at the weekend. The girl was raped and hatched to death by a rape gang at a church mission building in Idi-Ori, Ibadan, Oyo State. The gang rapists flee after their evil mission.
The victim, Grace Oshiagwu,Â 21 years, was identified as a National Diploma student of Oke Ogun Polytechnic, Saki. She hatched to death with machetes on Saturday by identified persons after being raped.
The 21 years old GraceOshiagwu is the third girlkilled in rape and murder circumstances in the same part of Ibadan, Oyo State. The rape and murder of GraceOshiagwu was said to have occurredtwo weeks after two similar incident occurred in the same area.
The Oyo State Police Command had commenced manhunt of the killers and rapists in the state, appealing to the public to support the Police with information.